Description:

Let's Dance, a video game starring Mel B, the former Spice Girl, and is the only party game that allows you to see yourself on the TV screen, dancing "on stage" along with other professional dancers, thanks to the body sensing technology. It has 28 tracks, with timeless classics and current hits such as Rihanna, Lady Gaga, Fergie, Spandau Ballet and Gloria Gaynor and others.
